data.description: Regular Sale! This beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom, 1800 SF home is located on a quite cul-de-sac of nicely kept homes in a quiet, well-established neighborhood. The extra large family room gives you a great place to entertain or let the kids play. Great layout, new tile floors, new bathrooms, new wall to wall carpeting, new paint and much more. Its ready for you...move in before the holidays! Brokered And Advertised By: Owners Equity Listing Agent: M. Satterwhite
